(7, 1, 'Submission', 'to be announced', '<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #7a7a7a; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: lighter; color: #353535; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 2rem;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; font-size: 0.9rem;\">:: Upload your paper</strong></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #7a7a7a; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem 2rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; list-style-position: outside; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">All authors should prepare full versions of papers in Microsoft Word (DOC) or Portable Document Format (PDF). Papers must be limited to six pages, including text, references, tables and figures.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The paper should follow the&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000ff; line-height: inherit; font-weight: bold; box-shadow: none;\" href=\"http://www.ieee.org/conferences_events/conferences/publishing/templates.html\">IEEE standard template</a><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000ff; line-height: inherit; font-weight: bold; box-shadow: none;\" href=\"http://www.ieee.org/conferences_events/conferences/publishing/templates.html\">.</a></span></span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Upload your paper at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.edas.info/N29152\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">https://www.edas.info/N29152</span></strong></a>.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Your final manuscript should be checked by PDF Express&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.pdf-express.org/\">https://www.pdf-express.org/</a> using the code&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">55644X</span></strong>&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">If you have any problem with submission, please do not hesitate to contact us at&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000ff; line-height: inherit; font-weight: bold; box-shadow: none;\" href=\"mailto:secretariat@ieee-icce.org\">secretariat@ieee-icce.org</a></span>.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;\">:: Conference review and submission policies</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem 2rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; list-style-position: outside; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Papers are reviewed on the basis that they do not contain plagiarized material and have not been submitted to any other conference at the same time (double submission).</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;\">PLEASE NOTE</strong> : To be published in the ICCE 2022 Conference Proceedings and IEEE Xplore, an author of an accepted paper is required to register for the conference and must present the paper at the conference.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;\">:: Publications</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem 2rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; list-style-position: outside; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Full regular papers will be submitted for inclusion into&nbsp;IEEEXplore, while poster papers are <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>not forwarded</strong></span> to IEEEXplore but will be included in the conference&rsquo;s proceedings. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit;\">:: Important dates</strong></span></p>\r\n<table style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; height: 150px;\" width=\"925\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: 30px;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(37, 37, 37, 0.1); height: 30px; width: 548.516px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&bull; Extended submissions Deadline:</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(37, 37, 37, 0.1); height: 30px; width: 375.484px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff0000;\">April 08th, 2022 - </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-decoration-line: line-through; color: #993300;\">Feb 28th , 2022</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: 30px;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(37, 37, 37, 0.1); height: 30px; width: 548.516px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&bull; Acceptance notification:</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(37, 37, 37, 0.1); height: 30px; width: 375.484px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;\">May 30th, 2022</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: 30px;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(37, 37, 37, 0.1); height: 30px; width: 548.516px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&bull; Registration and camer