trong><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: windowtext;\">June 21, 2022</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> and </span><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: windowtext;\">July 10, 2022</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> the cancellation is possible subject to an administration fee of 75% of the payment made.<br />c) Cancellation after </span><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: windowtext;\">July 10, 2022</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> no refund is possible.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #212529; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Regular as well as student registrations include: coffee breaks, 01 USB proceedings, lunches, gala dinner and attending all tutorials and technical sessions.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #212529; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Authors eligible for student registration should provide a valid student identity card or whatever certified evidence.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #212529; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Travel Information is available at&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://ieee-icce.org/p/visa-hotel-and-travel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #007bff;\">https://ieee-icce.org/p/visa-hotel-and-travel</span></a></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #212529; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">All IEEE ICCE 2022 participants are kindly requested to have travel insurance when entering Vietnam.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #212529; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Visas are generally required when entering Vietnam. Participants should check Embassy of Vietnam in their country to know if a visa is needed. Participants must hold visa for conference purpose. Therefore, please let us know in the registration form whether you will need a visa. For further information, please visit:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://ieee-icce.org/p/visa-hotel-and-travel\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #007bff;\">https://ieee-icce.org/p/visa-hotel-and-travel</span></a></span></li>\r\n</ol>', NULL, 'registration', NULL, NULL, 'ACTIVE', '2022-04-11 21:07:57', '2022-08-10 20:41:55');
